 Experience|first=Anne|last=Lewis|date=July 10, 2013|website=[[Ubisoft]]|archivedate=July 12, 2013|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130712221431/http://blog.ubi.com/watch-dogs-disrupt-engine-multiplayer/|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Kain-Aug2013\">{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2013/08/20/sony-and-ubisoft-team-up-on-watch-dogs-feature-film/#4370b5c23522|title=Sony And Ubisoft Team Up On 'Watch Dogs' Feature Film|first=Erik|last=Kain|date=August 20, 2013|website=[[Forbes]]|archivedate=October 12, 2017|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20171012192111/https://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2013/08/20/sony-and-ubisoft-team-up-on-watch-dogs-feature-film/%234370b5c23522#4370b5c23522|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Leack-Aug2013\">{{cite web|url=http://www.craveonline.com/site/561331-golden-joystick-awards-announces-game-of-the-year-2013-nominees|title=Golden Joystick Awards Announces Game of the Year 2013 Nominees|first=Jonathan|last=Leack|date=August 29, 2013|website=[[CraveOnline]]|archivedate=January 11, 2018|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20180111221858/http://www.craveonline.com/site/561331-golden-joystick-awards-announces-game-of-the-year-2013-nominees|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Griffiths-Sep2013\">{{cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/danielnyegriffiths/2013/09/04/jonathan-morin-creative-director-of-watch-dogs-interviewed-surveillance-and-the-city/2/#69fb66b2275d|title=Jonathan Morin, Creative Director of 'Watch Dogs', Interviewed: Surveillance And The City|first=Daniel|last=Nye Griffiths|date=September 4, 2013|website=[[Forbes]]|archivedate=January 11, 2018|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20180111235304/https://www.forbes.com/sites/danielnyegriffiths/2013/09/04/jonathan-morin-creative-director-of-watch-dogs-interviewed-surveillance-and-the-city/2/%2369fb66b2275d#69fb66b2275d|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Makuch-Oct2013\">{{cite web|url=https://www.gamespot.com/articles/watch-dogs-delayed-to-spring-2