 Copies, Helping Ubisoft Sales Rise Sharply|first=Eddie|last=Makuch|date=October 30, 2014|website=[[GameSpot]]|archivedate=October 31, 2014|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20141031090516/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/watch-dog-ships-9-million-copies-helping-ubisoft-s/1100-6423279/|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Ubisoft-Feb2015\">{{cite web|url=https://www.ubisoftgroup.com/comsite_common/en-US/images/pressrelease_downloadablemm_20150212_050959_ubisoftq3fy15englishfinaltcm99193930.pdf|title=Ubisoft\u00ae reports third quarter 2014-15 sales|author=[[Ubisoft]]|date=February 12, 2015|archivedate=January 10, 2018|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20180110231003/https://www.ubisoftgroup.com/comsite_common/en-US/images/pressrelease_downloadablemm_20150212_050959_ubisoftq3fy15englishfinaltcm99193930.pdf|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NAVGTR-Feb2015\">{{cite web|url=http://navgtr.org/archives/2445/|title=2014 NAVGTR Winners: Dragon 5, Alien/Mordor/South Park 4|date=February 16, 2015|website=[[NAVGTR]]|archivedate=February 17, 2015|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150217093448/http://navgtr.org/archives/2445/|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Phillips-Jun2016\">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-06-07-watch-dogs-2-launches-november-set-in-san-francisco|title=Watch Dogs 2 launches November, set in San Francisco|first=Tom|last=Phillips|date=June 7, 2016|website=[[Eurogamer]]|archivedate=June 7, 2016|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160607134514/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-06-07-watch-dogs-2-launches-november-set-in-san-francisco|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Takahashi-Oct2016\">{{cite web|url=https://venturebeat.com/2016/10/26/ubisoft-researcher-scouted-watch-dogs-2-by-hanging-out-with-hacktivists-in-sf-and-defcon/|title=Ubisoft researcher scouted Watch Dogs 2 by hanging out with hacktivists in SF and DefCon|first=Dean|last=Takahashi|date=October 26, 2016|website=[[GamesBeat]]|archivedate=November 24, 2016|archiveurl=https:/